::{{A|VO vo ambient w0 greeting zaowuJ 101.ogg}} {{A|VO vo ambient w0 greeting zaowuJ 102.ogg}} '''Exemplary:''' It's chaotic and dangerous outside. Here, it's different. You feel safe here, don't you?
