::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Can you reach them?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500016707-->
:::'''Exemplary:''' What do you mean? I'm a life created by the honorable Miss Ruan Mei, and the size of my paws has nothing to do with my capabilities. If you know my reaction speed and hidden talents, you'll be blown away.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_500016708-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500016708-->
